name: Jello Quest
description:
You work for Space Jello Corp, and aliens have taken your entire stock! You'll have to go on a short adventure to get it back! There are 3 enemies and if you fail to avoid their attacks, the Jello industry will be changed forever! Arrow Keys to Move.
